<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="14May1937"><font color="red">14 May 1937</font> <i>NLJL</i> (from G. Wren Howard to Paul L&eacute;on): Our reader has now finished his comparison of the Odyssey Press &hellip; John Lane &hellip; ULYSSES, and I send you his further list of queries which I hope Mr Joyce will be able to deal with. </div>
